==反響==
=== 評論 ===
這部作品得到了廣泛的讚譽，主要是關於勇利與維克托之間的關係，而其它的角色也頗受好評。[[動畫新聞網|動畫新聞網]]的James Beckett將尤里選為2016年動畫中的最佳角色之一<ref>{{cite web|last=The Anime News Network Editorial Team|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/feature/2016-12-27/the-best-characters-of-2016/.110384|title=The Best Characters of 2016|publisher=Anime News Network|date=December 27, 2016|accessdate=December 27, 2016|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115224514/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/feature/2016-12-27/the-best-characters-of-2016/.110384}}</ref>；Charapedia舉行的2016年最有吸引力的動畫角色調查中，維克托排名第4，勇利排名12，尤里排名19<ref>{{cite web|last=Green|first=Scott|url=http://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-news/2016/12/24/japanese-fans-pick-2016s-most-magnetic-anime-characters|title=Japanese Fans Pick 2016's Most Magnetic Anime Characters|publisher=Crunchyroll|date=December 24, 2016|accessdate=December 28, 2016|archive-date=2016-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161225132248/http://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-news/2016/12/24/japanese-fans-pick-2016s-most-magnetic-anime-characters|dead-url=no}}</ref>。角色的國籍和種族的多元性招來好評，而動畫的品質則毀譽參半<ref>{{cite web|last=Cirugeda|first=Kevin|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/feature/2016-11-09/the-biggest-animation-highlights-of-fall-2016/.108637|title=The Biggest Animation Highlights of Fall 2016|publisher=Anime News Network|date=November 9, 2016|accessdate=December 22, 2016|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220132919/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/feature/2016-11-09/the-biggest-animation-highlights-of-fall-2016/.108637|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uk-anime.net/anime/Yuri!!!_on_Ice_-_Eps._1-3.html|title=ANIME REVIEW: Yuri!!! On Ice - Eps. 1-3|last=Harker|first=Clover|publisher=UK Anime Network|date=December 15, 2016|accessdate=December 22, 2016|archive-date=2016-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161223132122/http://www.uk-anime.net/anime/Yuri%21%21%21_on_Ice_-_Eps._1-3.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Kotaku">{{cite web|last=D'Anastasio|first=Cecilia|url=http://kotaku.com/yuri-on-ice-the-kotaku-review-1790636052|title=Yuri On Ice: The Kotaku Review|publisher=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|date=December 30, 2016|accessdate=January 1, 2017|archive-date=2017-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170101042237/http://kotaku.com/yuri-on-ice-the-kotaku-review-1790636052|dead-url=no}}</ref>。動畫新聞網的團隊撰文評論2016年秋季最佳與最糟的動畫，而九位評論員中有五位都將《Yuri!!! on ICE》選為最佳作品<ref>{{cite web|last=The Anime News Network Editorial Team|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/feature/2016-12-23/the-best-and-worst-anime-of-fall-2016/.110280|title=The Best and Worst Anime of Fall 2016|publisher=Anime News Network|date=December 23, 2016|accessdate=December 23, 2016|archive-date=2016-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161223211015/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/feature/2016-12-23/the-best-and-worst-anime-of-fall-2016/.110280|dead-url=no}}</ref>；然而、對花式滑冰的技巧術語缺乏適當的說明<ref name="Anime UK News 1">{{cite web|last=Wolf|first=Ian|url=http://site.animeuknews.info/2016/11/24/streaming-review-of-yuri-on-ice-episodes-1-8-crunchyroll/|title=Streaming review of Yuri!!! On Ice, Episodes 1-8 (Crunchyroll)|publisher=Anime UK News|date=November 24, 2016|accessdate=December 22, 2016|archive-date=2017-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106145954/http://site.animeuknews.info/2016/11/24/streaming-review-of-yuri-on-ice-episodes-1-8-crunchyroll/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、動畫的品質良莠不齊和[[兼用卡|重複性過高]]也讓它受到負評<ref name="Kotaku"/>。

