=== 流行 ===
動畫吸引了大量的線上支持者。根據[[角川Ascii綜合研究所|角川Ascii綜合研究所]]的訊息趨勢分析顯示，在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上有144萬596條關於《Yuri!!! on ICE》的文章或留言，是該季的動畫中最多的，比第二名《[[排球少年！！|排球少年！！]]》的34萬8109則高出了一百一十萬。<ref>{{cite web|last=Pineda|first=Rafael Antonio|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2016-12-21/yuri-on-ice-dominates-fall-anime-on-twitter-rankings/.110186|title=Yuri!!! on Ice Dominates Fall Anime on Twitter Rankings|publisher=Anime News Network|date=December 21, 2016|accessdate=December 22, 2016|archive-date=2016-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222033930/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2016-12-21/yuri-on-ice-dominates-fall-anime-on-twitter-rankings/.110186|dead-url=no}}</ref> 此外、在第一季最後一集播出的那一天，[[Crunchyroll|Crunchyroll]]網站的串流服務癱瘓，推測是因為高頻率的網路活動導致<ref name="Anime UK News 2">{{cite web|last=Wolf|first=Ian|url=http://site.animeuknews.info/2016/12/22/streaming-review-of-yuri-on-ice-episodes-9-12-crunchyroll/|title=Streaming review of Yuri!!! On Ice, Episodes 9-12 (Crunchyroll)|publisher=Anime UK News|date=December 22, 2016|accessdate=December 22, 2016|archive-date=2017-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170102021535/http://site.animeuknews.info/2016/12/22/streaming-review-of-yuri-on-ice-episodes-9-12-crunchyroll/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。Crunchyroll發佈的數據顯示，《Yuri!!! on ICE》在[[台灣|台灣]]、[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]、[[越南|越南]]、[[寮國|寮國]]、[[新加坡|新加坡]]、[[波蘭|波蘭]]、[[捷克|捷克]]、[[獅子山共和國|獅子山共和國]]、[[布吉納法索|布吉納法索]]、[[馬拉威|馬拉威]]和[[波札那|波札那]]最受歡迎，不過它並不是這一季中最受歡迎的動畫，最受歡迎的是《[[Re:從零開始的異世界生活|Re:從零開始的異世界生活]]》。<ref>{{cite web|last=Thomas|first=Miles|url=http://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-feature/2016/12/29-1/feature-crunchyrolls-most-popular-anime-of-2016-by-country|title=FEATURE: Crunchyroll's Most Popular Anime of 2016 by Country!|publisher=Crunchyroll|date=December 29, 2016|accessdate=December 30, 2016|archive-date=2018-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181023212559/https://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-feature/2016/12/29-1/feature-crunchyrolls-most-popular-anime-of-2016-by-country|dead-url=no}}</ref>

